data.description: Property is zoned R2.5 for future development, Buyer to complete due diligence. Property has Verizon station contract for $1,150.96 a month with a 3% yearly increase. This zoning allows for 1 lot per 2500 sq ft, row-houses, duplexes, triplexes four-plexes and ADU's. New lots that are at least 5,000 square feet in area could also be developed with a cottage cluster. The property is located in a desirable area that offers easy access to schools, parks, shopping, and entertainment. With its generous size, this lot provides ample space for a range of development possibilities.33.110 (starting on page 110-36):
